          "id": "x-nikunj-2026-07-14-p2-s1",
          "text": "Introducing the Ramp-Autofill skill ✍️ > finds receipts automatically from your iMessage & Gmail. if it's in a link, it'll use playwright to convert the web page into a pdf and attach to the receipt automatically. > fills in memos on who you were meeting using your google calendar events. > understands your style of writing memos and categorization required by your organization by reviewing past transactions. it will then auto categorize all the missing transactions. > verifies it's work, flags any discrepancies and makes it easy to run as a scheduled job so you never have to look at expenses again.",
